text: "Spellbound" is a 1981 song by British gothic rock band Siouxsie and the Banshees and taken from their fourth studio album Juju. It went to number 22 in the United Kingdom and number 47 in New Zealand. == Track listing == ; 7" ; 12" == References == Category:1981 songs Category:Siouxsie and the Banshees songs Category:Glam rock songs
